Who is anyone here or anywhere else to say if one person's opinions are better or more valid then someone elses. This is a site dedicated to free speech, so its kind of hypocritical to say that anyone can share anything they want, but then in the next sentence slam someone for their comment, whatever it might be. If you dont like the movie dont download it, if you dont like the comment, so what, move on or leave your own comment, about the movie. But to insult that person because of their opinion is just childish and it really does show your age, and that alot of the torrent sites lately are filled with kids in the 12-17 range. Most grown men dont respond with douchy comments because someone else gave an uploader a -1. He's probably 13, and like the other guy said, he could just be jealous that he cant upload any of his own movies. Who knows, who cares. Is it even worth spending time on? Bone is a big boy, if he really cares that much let him respond on his own. I dont think he needs people coming to his rescue...
